code: @Override public Serializable[][] getParameterValues() {     double maxElemCount = (maxVal - minVal) + 1.     int numBatches = new Double(Math.ceil(maxElemCount / fetchSize)).intValue().     Serializable[][] parameters = new Serializable[numBatches][2].     int batchIndex = 0.     for (long start = minVal. start <= maxVal. start += fetchSize, batchIndex++) {         long end = start + fetchSize - 1.         if (end > maxVal) {             end = maxVal.         }         parameters[batchIndex] = new Long[] { start, end }.     }     return parameters. }
